<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>주문 취소됨 - Giftrue</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="bg-white shadow-sm border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Giftrue</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">인물 피규어 기념패 제작 서비스</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div class="bg-red-50 px-6 py-4 border-b border-red-200">
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-red-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.964-.833-2.732 0L4.082 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-red-800">주문이 취소되었습니다</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-red-600">이 주문은 더 이상 진행되지 않습니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content Section -->
      <div class="px-6 py-6">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Order Info -->
          <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 bg-gray-50">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">주문 정보</h3>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-600">주문번호:</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-gray-900"><%= @order.naver_order_number %></span>
              </div>
              <% if @order.orderer_name.present? %>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-600">주문자:</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-900"><%= @order.orderer_name %></span>
                </div>
              <% end %>
              <% if @order.cancelled_at.present? %>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-600">취소일시:</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-900"><%= @order.cancelled_at.strftime('%Y년 %m월 %d일 %H:%M') %></span>
                </div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cancellation Reason -->
          <% if @order.cancellation_reason.present? %>
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">취소 사유</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><%= @order.cancellation_reason %></p>
            </div>
          <% end %>

          <!-- Information Message -->
          <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-800">안내 사항</h3>
                <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-blue-700">
                  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                    <li>취소된 주문은 복구할 수 없습니다.</li>
                    <li>새로운 주문을 원하시면 다시 주문 과정을 진행해주세요.</li>
                    <li>문의사항이 있으시면 고객센터로 연락해주세요.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Information -->
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-6">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">고객센터 정보</h3>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <p>문의사항이 있으시면 언제든지 연락해주세요.</p>
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">📞 고객센터: 1588-0000</p>
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">📧 이메일: support@giftrue.com</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">운영시간: 평일 09:00 - 18:00 (주말, 공휴일 휴무)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors">
        <svg class="h-4 w-4 mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
        </svg>
        메인 페이지로 돌아가기
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>